events.name: UX TL;DR MEETUP #1
events.description:
Have you ever come across something new, had the browser tab open for weeks, but never found time to research it? Use this event as an excuse to dig a little deeper.

Join to level-up your design and research knowledge, meet other UXers, or learn about the methods used by designers and researchers at the venue.

6:30 PM - Arrival, seating, & drinks
7:15 PM - Intro talk by the host
7:30 PM - R&D: random team assignment, choose a topic, learn something new
9:00 PM - Q&A: share what your team learned
9:30 PM - The end
